rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Expression properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators with the domain of RDA Expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridged as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that shortens the source entity without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgementOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridgement of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been abridged, i.e., shortened without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abridger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by shortening or condensing the original work but leaving the nature and content of the original work substantially unchanged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that incorporates another entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been incorporated into another entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedInPartByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that incorporates part of the content of another entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedInPartExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been partially incorporated into another entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work (an abstracting and indexing service) that abstracts the contents of a source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that abbreviates the source entity in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been abstracted, i.e., abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractsForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracts for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose contents have been abstracted by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accessibilityContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accessibility content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to content that assists those with a sensory impairment in the greater understanding of content which their impairment prevents them fully seeing or hearing.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adaptation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that modifies the source entity for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a motion picture (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a motion picture based on the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a motion picture screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of the screenplay for a motion picture, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioProgramExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a radio program (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a radio program based on the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioScriptExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a radio script (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of the script for a radio program, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of the screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionProgramExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a television program (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a television program based on the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a television screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of the screenplay for a television program, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoProgramExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a video (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a video based on the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as a video screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of the screenplay for a video, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that modifies the source entity for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of brief additional material, less extensive than a supplement, but essential to the completeness of the text of the predominant work; it is usually added at the end of the content, but is sometimes issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work to which is added brief additional material, less extensive than a supplement, but essential to the completeness of the content of the work; it is usually added at the end of the content but is sometimes issued separately from it.

rdf:Description.reg:name: additionalScaleInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has additional scale information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to supplemental information about scale such as a statement of comparative measurements or limitation of the scale to particular parts of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysed in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that examines the source entity to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysisOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysis of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been examined to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: animator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has animator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a moving image work or computer program by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendixExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that forms an augmenting part of another work which is not essential to the completeness of the content, such as a list of references, statistical tables, and explanatory matter; it can be material which either comes at the end of the content of the predominant work, or is issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendixToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a predominant work that is augmented by another work that consists of material that is not essential to the completeness of the content, such as a list of references, statistical tables, and explanatory matter; the augmenting work can either come at the end of the content, or be issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangerOfMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has arranger of music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a musical work by rewriting the composition for a medium of performance different from that for which the work was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: An arranger of music may also modify the work for the same medium of performance, etc., keeping the musical substance of the original composition essentially unchanged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has art director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by overseeing the artists and craftspeople who build the sets for moving image productions.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artisticAndOrTechnicalCredit
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has artistic and/or technical credit
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a listing of persons, families, or corporate bodies making contributions to the artistic and/or technical production of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: aspectRatio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has aspect ratio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the ratio of the width to the height of a moving image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmentation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content is added to by another entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentedByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmented by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that adds to the content of a predominant entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: award
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has award
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a formal recognition of excellence, etc., given by an award- or prize-granting body, for the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression used as the basis for a derivative entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basisForLibrettoExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is basis for libretto (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cadenzaComposedForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza composed for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work such as a concerto for which an ornamental passage for a soloist has been composed, either by the same or a different composer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cadenzaExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work consisting of an ornamental passage for a soloist, added to a musical work such as a concerto, either by the same or a different composer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographerExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has cartographer (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing additional cartography, or by modifying the previous cartography.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogueExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is catalogue (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of a complete enumeration of items arranged systematically.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogueOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is catalogue of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a catalogue, i.e., a complete enumeration of items arranged systematically.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographerExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has choreographer (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing additional choreography, or by modifying the previous choreography.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographyExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreography (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of dance based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographyForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreography for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a derivative work consisting of dance.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colour content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the presence of colour, tone, etc., in the content of a resource. colour content is also the specific colours, tones, etc., (including black and white) present in the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourContentOfResourceDesignedForPersonsWithVisualImpairments
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colour content of resource designed for persons with visual impairments
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the presence of colour, tone, etc., in a resource designed for persons with visual impairments. colour content of resources designed for persons with visual impairments is also the specific colours, tones, etc., (excluding black and white) present in a resource designed for persons with visual impairments.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourOfMovingImage
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colour of moving image
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the presence of colour, tone, etc., in a moving image or images contained in a resource. colour of moving image is also the specific colours, tones, etc., (including black and white) present in a moving image or images contained in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourOfStillImage
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colour of still image
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the presence of colour, tone, etc., in a still image or images contained in a resource. colour of still image is also the specific colours, tones, etc., (including black and white) present in a still image or images contained in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: colourOfThreeDimensionalForm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has colour of three-dimensional form
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the presence of colour, tone, etc., in a three-dimensional form or forms contained in a resource. colour of three-dimensional form is also the specific colours, tones, etc., (including black and white) present in a three-dimensional form or forms contained in a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on the described entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a set of explanatory or critical notes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commentator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium.

rdf:Description.reg:name: complementedByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is complemented by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work paired with another entity without either entity being considered to predominate.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composerExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has composer (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression by adding music to a work that originally lacked it, by composing new music to substitute for the original music, or by composing new music to supplement the existing music.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordanceExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of an index of all the words in the predominant entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordanceToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a concordance, i.e., an index of all the words in the predominant entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: conductor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has conductor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a musical work by leading a performing group (orchestra, chorus, opera, etc.) in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contained in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a larger work of which a part is a discrete component.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contains (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is a discrete component of a larger entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contentType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has content type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a categorization reflecting the fundamental form of communication in which the content is expressed and the human sense through which it is intended to be perceived.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: For content expressed in the form of an image or images, content type also reflects the number of spatial dimensions in which the content is intended to be perceived and the perceived presence or absence of movement.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content continues an earlier entity under a new title.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedInPartByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued in part by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work part of whose content separated from an earlier entity to form a new entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuesExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continues (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is continued by the content of a later entity under a new title.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuesInPartExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continues in part (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that split into two or more separate entities with new titles.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contributor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has contributor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Contributors include editors, translators, arrangers of music, performers, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: costumeDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has costume designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by designing the costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtReporter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has court reporter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by preparing a courts opinions for publication.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiquedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critiqued in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that contains a critical evaluation of the described entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiqueOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critique of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a critical evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dancer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dancer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by dancing in a musical, dramatic, etc., presentation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfCapture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a date or range of dates associated with the capture (i.e., recording, filming, etc.) of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the earliest date associated with an expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: derivativeExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is derivative expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression that is a modification of a source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: describedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is described in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression that describes a described entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descriptionOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is description of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression described by a describing entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that systematically and comprehensively condenses the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been digested, i.e., systematically and comprehensively condensed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: draftsman
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has draftsman
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by an architect, inventor, etc., by making detailed plans or drawings for buildings, ships, aircraft, machines, objects, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dramatizationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dramatization of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as a drama.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dramatizedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dramatized as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a dramatic work adapted from the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dubbedVersion
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dubbed version
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a moving image work that translates the spoken dialogue of the original work into a different language.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dubbedVersionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dubbed version of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a moving image work in which the spoken dialogue has been translated into a language different from that of the original work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: duration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has duration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the playing time, running time, etc., of the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Duration also includes performance time for a resource containing notated music or notated movement.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has editor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by revising or clarifying the content, e.g., adding an introduction, notes, or other critical matter.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: An editor may also prepare an expression of a work for production, publication, or distribution.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorOfMovingImageWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has editor of moving image work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for assembling, arranging, and trimming film, video, or other moving image formats, including both visual and audio aspects.

rdf:Description.reg:name: errataExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is errata (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of errors discovered after the publication of the predominant work, with their corrections.

rdf:Description.reg:name: errataToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is errata to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is augmented by a list of errors in the predominant work, discovered after publication, with their corrections.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluatedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluated in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that examines or judges the described entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is examined or judged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expandedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is expanded as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that enlarges upon the content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expandedVersionOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is expanded version of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a derivative work that enlarges upon the content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: findingAidExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is finding aid (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides a guide to the organization, arrangement, and contents of an archival collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: findingAidForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is finding aid for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of an archival collection that is described in a finding aid, i.e., a guide to the organization, arrangement, and contents of the collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formatOfNotatedMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has format of notated music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to format of notated music is the musical or physical layout of the content of a resource that is presented in the form of musical notation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfMusicalNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of musical notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a set of characters and/or symbols used to express the musical content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfNotatedMovement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of notated movement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a set of characters and/or symbols used to express the movement content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a set of characters and/or symbols used to express the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfTactileNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of tactile notation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a set of characters and/or symbols used to express the content of a resource in a form that can be perceived through touch.

rdf:Description.reg:name: freelyTranslatedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is freely translated as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that freely translates the text into another language, preserving the spirit of the original, but not its linguistic details.

rdf:Description.reg:name: freeTranslationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is free translation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been translated freely, preserving the spirit of the original, but not its linguistic details.

rdf:Description.reg:name: guideExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is guide (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that guides a user through the use of the predominant work, using notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: guideToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is guide to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is augmented by another work consisting of material to help the user of the predominant work, such as notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: horizontalScaleOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has horizontal scale of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the ratio of horizontal distances in the cartographic content of a resource to the actual distances they represent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: host
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has host
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by leading a program (often broadcast) that includes other guests, performers, etc. (e.g., talk show host).

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForTheExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a character string uniquely associated with an expression, or with a surrogate for an expression (e.g., an authority record).
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The identifier serves to differentiate that expression from other expressions.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrationsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of pictorial content designed to explain or decorate the augmented entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrationsForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is augmented by pictorial content designed to explain or decorate it.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrativeContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illustrative content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to content designed to illustrate the primary content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illustrator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by supplementing the primary content with drawings, diagrams, photographs, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: imitatedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitated as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that copies the style or content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: imitationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose style or content is copied in a derivative work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incidentalMusicExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work that that provides the incidental music for a play or other spoken work for the stage.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incidentalMusicForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work such as a play or other spoken work for the stage that uses the musical work as incidental music.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexed in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work (an abstracting and indexing service) that indexes the contents of a source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of the predominant entity, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexingForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexing for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose contents have been indexed by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for an index, i.e., a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of the predominant entity, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: instrumentalist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has instrumentalist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by playing a musical instrument.

rdf:Description.reg:name: intervieweeExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewee (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: interviewerExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewer (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: languageOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a language in which a work is expressed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: languageOfTheContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has language of the content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a language used to express the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work such as an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, that uses the text of the related work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manifestationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manifestation of expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a physical embodiment of an expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mediumOfPerformanceOfMusicalContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance of musical content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the instrument, instruments, voice, voices, etc., used (or intended to be used) for performance of musical content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergedToFormExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merged to form (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression which brings the expression together with another expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergerOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merger of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to one of the expressions which come together to form the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: minuteTaker
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has minute taker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body, responsible for recording the minutes of a meeting.

rdf:Description.reg:name: moderator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has moderator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by leading a program (often broadcast) where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureAdaptationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture adaptation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureScreenplayBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalArrangement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical arrangement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that rewrites the source entity for a medium of performance different from that for which the work was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalArrangementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical arrangement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been rewritten for a medium of performance different from that for which the work was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has musical director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by coordinating the activities of the composer, the sound editor, and sound mixers for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalSettingExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical setting (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio, that uses the text of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalSettingOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical setting of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text for a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalVariationsBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical variations based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work from which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalVariationsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical variations (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work in which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken from the source work to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

rdf:Description.reg:name: narrator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has narrator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by reading or speaking in order to give an account of an act, occurrence, course of events, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnChangesInContentCharacteristics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in content characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a note on changes in content characteristics that occur in subsequent issues or parts of a resource issued in successive parts or between iterations of an integrating resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an annotation providing additional information about content recorded as an expression attribute.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelizationExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a novel adapted from the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelizationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as a novel.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onScreenPresenter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has on-screen presenter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by appearing on screen to provide contextual or background information.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: An on-screen presenter may appear in nonfiction moving image materials or in introductions to fiction moving image materials.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherDetailsOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other details of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to mathematical data and other features of the cartographic content of a resource not recorded in statements of scale, projection, and coordinates.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherDistinguishingCharacteristicOfTheExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other distinguishing characteristic of the expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a characteristic other than content type, language of expression, or date of expression.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: It serves to differentiate an expression from another expression of the same work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: panelist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has panelist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by participating in a program (often broadcast) where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.

rdf:Description.reg:name: paraphrasedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is paraphrased as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that restates the content of the source work in a different form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: paraphraseOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is paraphrase of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a paraphrase, i.e., a restating of the content of the source work in a different form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: parodiedAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is parodied as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that imitates the style or content of the source work for comic effect.

rdf:Description.reg:name: parodyOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is parody of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose style or content is imitated for comic effect.

rdf:Description.reg:name: performer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has performer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by performing music, acting, dancing, speaking, etc., often in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: performerNarratorAndOrPresenter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has performer, narrator, and/or presenter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for performing, narrating, and/or presenting a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: placeAndDateOfCapture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has place and date of capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the place and date associated with the capture (i.e., recording, filming, etc.) of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: placeOfCapture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has place of capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the place associated with the capture (i.e., recording, filming, etc.) of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: precededByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is preceded by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that precedes (e.g., is earlier in time or before in narrative) the succeeding entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: presenter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has presenter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body mentioned in an x presents credit for moving image materials and who is probably associated with production, finance, or distribution in some way.

rdf:Description.reg:name: productionDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has production designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for designing the overall visual appearance of a moving image production.

rdf:Description.reg:name: projectionOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has projection of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the method or system used to represent the surface of the earth or of a celestial sphere on a plane.

rdf:Description.reg:name: puppeteer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has puppeteer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by manipulating, controlling, or directing puppets or marionettes in a moving image production or a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioAdaptationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio adaptation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioScriptBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio script based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as the script for a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioScriptExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio script (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text for a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: recordingEngineer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has recording engineer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by supervising the technical aspects of a sound or video recording session.

rdf:Description.reg:name: recordist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has recordist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by using a recording device to capture sound and/or video during a recording session, including field recordings of natural sounds, folkloric events, music, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: relatedExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related expression
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression, represented by an identifier, an authorized access point, or a description, that is related to the expression being described (e.g., a revised version, a translation).

rdf:Description.reg:name: remadeAsExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remade as (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a new motion picture, radio program, television program, or video based on an earlier work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: remakeOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remake of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a new motion picture, radio program, television program, or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewedInExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reviewed in (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that contains a brief evaluation of the described entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is review of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a brief evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: revisedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is revised as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to n expression of a work that has been updated, corrected, or expanded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: revisionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is revision of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for an updated, corrected, or expanded version.

rdf:Description.reg:name: scale
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has scale
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the ratio of the dimensions of an image or three-dimensional form contained or embodied in a resource to the dimensions of the entity it represents.

rdf:Description.reg:name: scaleOfStillImageOrThreeDimensionalForm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has scale of still image or three-dimensional form
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the ratio of the dimensions of a still image or three-dimensional form contained or embodied in a resource to the dimensions of the entity it represents.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text for a motion picture, television program or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work such as a motion picture, television program, or video, that uses the text of the work as a screenplay.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTheMotionPictureExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for the motion picture (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTheTelevisionProgramExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for the television program (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTheVideoExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for the video (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: script
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a set of characters and/or symbols used to express the written language content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: scriptForTheRadioProgramExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is script for the radio program (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text of the source work as the script for a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: separatedFromExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is separated from (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that spun off a part of its content to form a new entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: singer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has singer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by using his/her/their voice, with or without instrumental accompaniment, to produce music.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A singers performance may or may not include actual words.

rdf:Description.reg:name: soundContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has sound content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the presence of sound in a resource other than one that consists primarily of recorded sound.

rdf:Description.reg:name: speaker
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has speaker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by speaking words, such as a lecture, speech, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: splitIntoExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is split into (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of one of two or more works resulting from the division of an earlier entity into separate entities.

rdf:Description.reg:name: stageDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has stage director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a stage work through the general management and supervision of a performance.

rdf:Description.reg:name: storyteller
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has storyteller
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by relaying a creators original story with dramatic or theatrical interpretation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: succeededByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is succeeded by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that succeeds (e.g., later in time or after in a narrative) the preceding entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: summarizationOfTheContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has summarization of the content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an abstract, summary, synopsis, etc., of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: summaryExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is summary (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of a brief recapitulation of the content of the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: summaryOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is summary of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work used as the basis for a brief recapitulation of its content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supersededByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is superseded by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a later entity used in place of the earlier entity, usually because the later entity contains updated or new information that makes the earlier entity obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supersededInPartByExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is superseded in part by (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a later entity used in part in place of the earlier entity, usually because the later entity contains updated or new information that makes part of the earlier entity obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supersedesExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supersedes (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of an earlier work whose content has been replaced by a later entity, usually because the later entity contains updated or new information that makes the earlier entity obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supersedesInPartExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supersedes in part (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of an earlier work whose content has been partially replaced by a later entity, usually because the later entity contains updated or new information that makes the earlier entity obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supplementaryContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has supplementary content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to content (e.g., an index, a bibliography, an appendix) designed to supplement the primary content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supplementExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supplement (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that updates or otherwise complements the predominant entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supplementToExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supplement to (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is updated or otherwise complemented by the augmenting entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: surveyor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has surveyor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a cartographic work by providing measurements or dimensional relationships for the geographic area represented.

rdf:Description.reg:name: teacher
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has teacher
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a performer contributing to an expression of a work by giving instruction or providing a demonstration.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionAdaptationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television adaptation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionScreenplayBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television screenplay based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: transcriber
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has transcriber
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by changing it from one system of notation to another.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translatedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translated as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that translates the text of the source entity into a language different from that of the original work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is translation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been translated, i.e., the text expressed in a language different from that of the original work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: translator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has translator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by expressing the original text of the work in a language different from that of the original work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A translator may also translate a text from an older form of a language into the modern form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verseAdaptationExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is verse adaptation (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a literary composition in verse form adapted from the source entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verseAdaptationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is verse adaptation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as a literary composition in verse form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verticalScaleOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has vertical scale of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the scale of elevation or vertical dimension of the cartographic content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoAdaptationOfExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video adaptation of (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted for video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoScreenplayBasedOnExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video screenplay based on (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoScreenplayExpression
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video screenplay (expression)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides the text for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: voiceActor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has voice actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to an actor contributing to an expression of a work by providing the voice for characters in radio and audio productions and for animated characters in moving image works, as well as by providing voice-overs in radio and television commercials, dubbed resources, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: workExpressed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has work expressed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to the work realized through an expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedCommentary
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of added commentary
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing an interpretation or critical explanation of the original work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedLyrics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of added lyrics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a writer of words added to an expression of a musical work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfAddedText
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of added text
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a primarily non-textual work by providing text for the non-textual work (e.g., writing captions for photographs, descriptions of maps).

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfIntroduction
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of introduction
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing an introduction to the original work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfPreface
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of preface
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing a preface to the original work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: writerOfSupplementaryTextualContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has writer of supplementary textual content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an expression to a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing supplementary textual content (e.g., an appendix, an introduction, a preface) to the original work.
